<paragraph id="5D7B0C6BFF91EF52FF12F9C5FAA2F916" blockId="57.[151,1436,1648,1711]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
This tribe includes 56 species in 12 genera and is exclusively Neotropical. Three genera and 10 species are currently recognized for 
<collectingCountry id="25D34CFBFF91EF52FEC4F921FE3CF916" box="[321,393,1684,1710]" name="Brazil" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. Here we record for the first time one species and one genus for the 
<collectingRegion id="9F00C289FF91EF52FB01F921FAA6F916" box="[1156,1299,1684,1710]" country="Brazil" name="Parana" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Paraná State</collectingRegion>
